@startuml journey-end-to-end
' ============================================================
' User-Experience Flow: Target-State End-to-End Journey
'
' Product/UX-clarity altitude (not an API sequence). Columns are the
' human/behind-the-scenes roles; node fill marks shipped vs planned so the
' aspirational loop doubles as a gap map.
'
' Primary path is child-initiated (target state). Rose-filled nodes are the
' parts of that loop not yet built (tracked in the R1 deployment review).
'
' Source screens / decisions:
'   frontend/src/router.tsx                         (kid + guardian route trees)
'   docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-30-phase-4a-mobile-ui-wireframes-design.md
'   docs/planning/adr/adr-005-mandatory-human-approval.md  (approval gate)
'   docs/architecture/diagrams/seq-generation.puml  (behind-the-scenes detail)
'   docs/architecture/diagrams/seq-offline.puml     (offline read + reconnect)
'   docs/architecture/diagrams/seq-reading-state.puml (sync reconciliation)
' ============================================================

title Target-State End-to-End User Journey\n(child-initiated; rose = planned, not yet built)

skinparam defaultFontName "Roboto"
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #5a3e28
skinparam ArrowFontColor #5a3e28
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #FFFDF8
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #8c6f56
skinparam ActivityBorderThickness 1
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #f8f3e8
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #8c6f56
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #F1E9D8
skinparam NoteBorderColor #c9b48f
skinparam swimlaneWidth same

' Swimlane column tints = who is acting (storybook palette, tokens.css)
|#F0D9B8|Child|
|#CDDCEC|Guardian|
|#C5D9CC|Admin|
|#E4E4E4|System|

' ============ Act 1: Guardian onboarding (once) ============
|Guardian|
start
:Sign in
(email/password, Google,
or Apple if enabled);
note right: /guardian/login  •  shipped
:Create each child's profile
(name + preset avatar);
note right: /guardian/profiles  •  shipped

' ============ The repeating story loop ============
repeat :a new story is wanted;

' ---- Act 2: Request (child-initiated primary path) ----
|Child|
:Open the app, tap my avatar;
note right: /  (Profile Picker)  •  shipped
#F3D9D4:Tap "I want a new story"
and say what it's about;
note right: planned
|Guardian|
#F3D9D4:See my child's request,
approve or tweak it;
note right: planned (request-approval)

' ---- Act 3: Behind the scenes ----
|System|
:Write the story
(staged, with fallback);
note right: generation pipeline  •  shipped\ndetail: seq-generation
:Safety check
(flags risky passages);
note right: validator gate  •  shipped
|Guardian|
:"My Requests" shows
"Generating...";
note right: /guardian/intake  •  shipped

' ---- Act 4: Human approval gate (ADR-005) ----
|Admin|
repeat :take the top item;
  :Open the review queue
  (Flagged, then Ready,
  then Still processing);
  note right: /guardian  (Console)  •  shipped
  :Read the flagged passages,
  then the full story;
  note right: /guardian/review/:id  •  shipped
backward:Send back with a note
-> the story is rewritten;
repeat while (Safe for a child?) is (no) not (yes -> approve)
:Approve
(recorded human gate, ADR-005);

' ---- Act 5: Assign ----
|Guardian|
:Assign it to the child
("Assign more" to add siblings);
note right: intake / assign  •  shipped
|Child|
:My avatar shows
"new story ready!";
note right: Profile Picker pill  •  shipped

' ---- Act 6: Read & rate ----
|Child|
:Open my Library
(Continue Reading + shelf);
note right: /library/:profileId  •  shipped
:Read passages,
make choices;
note right: /read/...  (Reader)  •  shipped
if (Online?) then (yes)
  :Progress saves as I go;
else (offline)
  :Read from cache,
  progress waits in a queue;
  note right: offline-first  •  shipped
  :On reconnect it syncs
  (reconcile if it clashes);
  note right: seq-offline / seq-reading-state
endif
:Reach an ending;
#F3D9D4:Rate the story;
note right: planned\n(completion + rating not\nyet recorded by the UI)

repeat while (Want another story?) is (yes) not (no)
|Child|
stop

legend bottom
  == Reading the journey ==
  Columns = who is acting: <b>Child</b>, <b>Guardian</b>, <b>Admin</b>, <b>System</b> (behind the scenes).
  |= Node |= Meaning |
  |<back:#FFFDF8>  white  </back>| Shipped in the app today |
  |<back:#F3D9D4>  rose   </back>| Planned target-state step, not yet built |
  The child-initiated request (Act 2) is the target-state entry point; today a
  guardian starts requests from the Intake page. Approval (ADR-005) is the one
  mandatory gate before any story reaches a child.
endlegend

@enduml
